Shanghai Builds Int ' l Conference Center
SHANGHAI , November 19 ( Xinhua ) -- Construction of the Shanghai International Conference Center is in full swing for a conference of the Top 500 multinational companies U.S . - based Fortune magazine lists in 1999 .
Construction is scheduled for completion in June next year , and the conference in September will be the first to be held in the conference center , which will feature 30 conference halls with total floor space of 32,000 square meters .
The largest multifunction hall covering 4,300 sq.m .
will hold 4,000 people for conferences and provide dining space for 3,000 people .
